{"tid":2201332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人去到某個年紀，就真係得返自己一個","createTime":"2020-09-13T17:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T17:22:31.000Z","uid":58316,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c4ec28f5a19f9b529d26ada10b92454f228f46","tid":2201332,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"以前睇過既卡通<br />\n鍾意過既卡通人物<br />\n曾經以為佢係自己<br />\n自己又係佢<br />\n睇過d書 電視劇 戲<br />\n見到d角色又諗乜咁似自己<br />\n原來都唔係好似<br />\n聽過d歌<br />\n聽個下有共鳴<br />\n但生活上發生左d事<br />\n又諗唱個個又何曾經歷過<br />\n以前都會諗<br />\n係咪自己自命不凡<br />\n始終人人條命都係咁<br />\n每朝搭地鐵一日咁多班一班咁多卡<br />\n自己只係一卡上面其中一個<br />\n人海裏面<br />\n冇咩邊個係冇佢唔得<br />\n或者咁講<br />\n正正係咁<br />\n死左都冇人理<br />\n就唔使再理人點睇<br />\n因為好似無論做咩<br />\n都唔會改變到d咩"},{"pid":"6973e8c7dfce3fcda01ac59ffac2a3285a1e198f","tid":2201332,"uid":619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"Ok........"},{"pid":"36bd9d9dc674beaa435e5be287ef53b8c77002ff","tid":2201332,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"巴打你幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a86a114a5082413d598f2568d803855e06c6df4","tid":2201332,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36bd9d9dc674beaa435e5be287ef53b8c77002ff","tid":2201332,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"巴打你幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"16碎=,="},{"pid":"712a7e5077d75dcdadbe7387f248b209de58182e","tid":2201332,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f13fd7cb620821d623ded7d741e76f4ee3900be7","tid":2201332,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a86a114a5082413d598f2568d803855e06c6df4","tid":2201332,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36bd9d9dc674b